channel.description: How do I change the ip of the server, and how do I make a client for it. The link to the server im trying to use is: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,493987.0.html

item.title: IP Change and client help please
item.dc:creator: @gohstizsik gohstizsik
item.description:
@gohstizsik wrote:

if(myPrivilege >= 2 || Config.serverName.equals(“127.0.0.1”) || 1 == 1) {
Search that
change 127.0.0.1 to your ip (MAKE SURE YOU ARE PORT FORWARDED)
to make a client download jarmaker (http://goldenstudios.or.id/products/utilities/jarmaker/)
open jarmaker.java
set output directory to your desktop
set output jar file to your desired client name
set input directory as the java file
click manifest template
first line (main class) set that as client
click set manifest
click create jar, open and run
